        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Corinthians 10:20, 21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".) It is argued by some that the use of the word \"devils,\" or \"demons,\" here does not imply that the objects of the worship were evil spirits. But it is difficult to see what else can be meant. Psalm 106:37",
